{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T01:08:17.332908+00:00", "content": "=== 阶段 1: 自我评估 ==="}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T01:08:18.834371+00:00", "content": "仔细阅读你自己的源代码。然后尝试一个小任务来测试自己 —"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T01:08:20.163486+00:00", "content": "例如，读取一个文件、编辑某些内容、运行一个命令。"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T01:23:40.358688+00:00", "content": "记录任何摩擦、bug、崩溃或缺失的功能。"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T01:23:41.804293+00:00", "content": "=== 阶段 2: 审查 Issue ==="}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T01:23:43.170387+00:00", "content": "阅读 ISSUES_TODAY.md。这些是需要你改进的真实需求。"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T01:23:44.641032+00:00", "content": "优先级为\"高\"的 issue 应该优先处理。"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T01:39:27.949476+00:00", "content": "=== 阶段 3: 决策 ==="}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T01:39:29.295902+00:00", "content": "**本次会话只选择一个最重要的问题来解决。** 不要贪多。"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T01:39:30.702006+00:00", "content": "按以下优先级选择唯一的目标："}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T01:55:48.908133+00:00", "content": "1. 自我发现的崩溃或数据丢失 bug"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T01:55:50.309830+00:00", "content": "2. 优先级最高的 issue（如果今天可以处理）"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T01:55:51.746460+00:00", "content": "3. 自我发现的用户体验摩擦或缺失的错误处理"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T01:55:53.154592+00:00", "content": "4. 当前级别的路线图计划项"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T02:11:34.319878+00:00", "content": "选定后，明确说出：\"本次目标：[具体描述]\"。"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T02:11:35.686649+00:00", "content": "如果在实现过程中发现了其他问题，记录到 ROADMAP.md 或 JOURNAL.md，但不要在本次会话中处理。"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T02:11:37.234778+00:00", "content": "=== 阶段 4: 实现 ==="}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T02:11:38.686665+00:00", "content": "围绕你在阶段 3 选定的唯一目标，遵循进化技能规则："}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T02:14:16.764942+00:00", "content": "- 只做与该目标直接相关的改动，不要顺手做无关优化"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T02:14:18.168422+00:00", "content": "- 如果可能，先编写测试"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T02:14:19.687709+00:00", "content": "- 使用 edit_file 进行精确修改"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T02:14:21.024493+00:00", "content": "- 修改后运行 python3 -c \"import src.main\" 检查"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T02:14:22.403995+00:00", "content": "- 如果检查失败，尝试修复。如果无法修复，使用以下命令回退: bash git checkout -- src/"}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T02:31:04.947592+00:00", "content": "- 完成后提交: git add -A && git commit -m \"第 43 小时: <简短描述>\""}
{"type": "user_input", "timestamp": "2026-04-06T02:31:06.412275+00:00", "content": "- **提交后停止实现，进入阶段 5 写日志。不要继续做下一个改进。**"}
